Class Plant

pkgMain.Plant

public class Plant
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Class - Plant, this class builds a plant object which has all the relevant information relating to a plant for this proejct such as ph size, type, color, an image associated with it.
Author:
William Cantera, Diane Vinson, Ben Testani, Jacob Kuchma, Maria Venrooy

  • Constructor Details

    • Plant

      public Plant​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String latinName, java.lang.String height, int width, java.lang.String description, java.lang.String waterUse, java.lang.String bloomSeason, java.lang.String flowerColor, java.lang.String soilpH, javafx.scene.image.Image plantPic, java.lang.String sunAmount, PlantType type)
      Custom constructor for plants
      Parameters:
      name - a String representing the name of the plant
      latinName - a String representing the Latin name of the plant
      height - a String representing the height of the plant
      width - an int representing the diameter of the plant in inches, used to make circle icon
      description - a String giving a description of the plant
      waterUse - a String representing how much water the plant needs
      bloomSeason - a String representing when the plant will begin to bloom
      flowerColor - a String representing the color of the plant's flowers
      soilpH - a String representing the soil pH that the plant prefers
      plantPic - an Image of the plant
      sunAmount - a String representing how much sun the plant prefers
      summerColor - a Color for the icon during the summer
      fallColor - a Color for the icon during the fall
      type - the PlantType that the Plant is
